{"tid":2302660,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"攬炒巴不停比人帶風向抹黑","createTime":"2020-11-27T09:41:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T11:58:02.000Z","uid":287577,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a522c8ee40892e060efd0b5b54c4e24f806e3e38","tid":2302660,"uid":287577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T09:41:37.000Z","msg":"話說我哩排好忙所以冇嘜課金<br />\n咁人唔課金錢就自然會多<br />\n岩先我打開銀包醒起好耐冇課金<br />\n咁就上離搜尋攬炒巴搵下有冇招父親啦<br />\n一㩒落去當堂嚇左跳！<br />\n攬炒巴夾帶私逃喎，咁我仲點課金喎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SApxRgG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSApxRgG.png&h=d5425900&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁我就唸住禁入去啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nv0EwfN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnv0EwfN.png&h=c1b9f08f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1HRMbfO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1HRMbfO.png&h=3e3e379b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CK6kfHu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCK6kfHu.png&h=9a5d88a0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YX7vCVQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYX7vCVQ.png&h=69985c3b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WBpqrPb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWBpqrPb.png&h=bef246a9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1HZt82x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1HZt82x.png&h=65956863&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yz6kfHy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyz6kfHy.png&h=6efc376a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然後就得啖笑<br />\n哦～原來有照薄嫁<br />\n成班五毛pr狗係度帶風向"},{"pid":"64a2ec3772cad4dc388e9ce94e69f1bdb21f41a1","tid":2302660,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T09:42:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3090aa7971e125521c99